{"tid":1777456,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩電來年加電費　消息指港燈加5.2%中電加2.5%","createTime":"2019-12-10T08:45:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T15:16:26.000Z","uid":57424,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a7d999c93f7d6374644b62e620fbc261c7c8c833","tid":1777456,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:45:17.000Z","msg":"兩電今(10日)將公布來年調升電費，香港電燈及中華電力下午將在立法會經濟發展事務委員會，交代明年電費調整幅度。消息指，兩電加幅均為單位數，港燈加幅為5.2%，而中電則加2.5%。<br />\n中電總裁蔣東強在會前見記者透露，明年將撥出2億港元紓困措施，支援中小企、貧困學生及弱勢社群，希望與市民共度時艱，盡量減輕電費調整對於市民壓力，稍後會在立法會講解計劃。<br />\n政府去年推出電費紓緩計劃，每戶每月可獲50港元補貼，今年8月政府再推出每戶2000港元的電費補貼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3daa9ebffea9dfd5736538598985bf0fefe9a83e","tid":1777456,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:57:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0539bbdfdd1ca9910087466de48539397124a5ac","tid":1777456,"uid":216709,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T09:06:14.000Z","msg":"信減免舒緩既on9, 只係將加價合理化同埋延後<br />\n到左2021年真正加價時,就無人會記得2019年12月既加價<br />\n同黨鐵一鳩樣"},{"pid":"68b98d4bfed27af9e35d3ad586d1031403f44481","tid":1777456,"uid":84081,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T09:09:38.000Z","msg":"燃料咁撚平都加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40cf1bc724fff67c2d0fefe8d13faa4f30344ac5","tid":1777456,"uid":83102,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T09:16:29.000Z","msg":"好似話未來打算轉曬做天然氣<br />\n應該黎緊瘋狂加價"},{"pid":"54efdbd788eb44c7d8664c1b1d3a3f70c3eaec77","tid":1777456,"uid":275238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T09:17:32.000Z","msg":"但股價派息唔加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cl